IN THE OTHER ROOM.

596
00:50:54,918 --> 00:50:58,905
[ Speaking Japanese ]

597
00:51:03,910 --> 00:51:05,912
[ Laughing ]

598
00:51:07,414 --> 00:51:09,416
THANK YOU.

599
00:51:11,918 --> 00:51:14,421
NICE GOING,
SAYING YOU'RE
MY FATHER.

