A RANGE OF TWO CITY BLOCKS.

615
00:52:21,404 --> 00:52:24,908
YOU CAN KNOCK OUT AN ARMY
AND REALLY KICK SOME ASS.
[ Doors Open ]

616
00:52:26,409 --> 00:52:28,912
