00:52:37,420 --> 00:52:40,407
SHE'S YOUR DAUGHTER?
THAT'S DEFINITE?
WHAT'S IT TO YOU?

618
00:52:40,407 --> 00:52:44,911
WHEN I SAID SHE LOOKED
LIKE YOU, I GUESS
I MIGHT HAVE BEEN WRONG.

619
00:52:44,911 --> 00:52:47,914
I-I MEAN, EXCEPT THE NOSE.
WHERE WERE WE?

620
00:52:47,914 --> 00:52:51,418
ANTI-PERSONNEL BAZOOKA
MADE IN KOREA.
IT CAN STOP A TANK.

621
00:52:51,418 --> 00:52:54,905
YOU GOT SOMETHING
I CAN USE IN TOWN?
