622
00:52:54,905 --> 00:52:58,909
A LITTLE MORE DISCREET.
SOMETHING NICE AND LIGHT.
FOR THE CITY.

623
00:52:58,909 --> 00:53:02,412
THIS IS A CLASSIC .357 MAGNUM.

624
00:53:02,412 --> 00:53:05,415
THE LATEST UZI. FIFTY ROUNDS
