00:53:28,905 --> 00:53:31,908
THIS ONE'S ARGENTINE.
COMES WITH ANTI-RIOT BULLETS.

634
00:53:32,409 --> 00:53:34,411
I BROUGHT SOME GRENADES
TO GO WITH IT.

635
00:53:34,911 --> 00:53:37,914
- I'M GOING TO TAKE THIS ONE.
- [ Sighs ]
  I KNEW YOU'D PICK THAT.

636
00:53:37,914 --> 00:53:41,418
YOU WANNA COUPLE
OF GRENADES JUST IN CASE?
NO, MAYBE LATER.

637
00:53:41,918 --> 00:53:45,405
WOULD SCARE THE GIRL.
I WANT TO TRY
TO KEEP THIS DISCREET.

638
00:53:45,405 --> 00:53:48,909
CAN YOU GIVE ME THE JUICE?
WELL, I DON'T KNOW MUCH.

639
00:53:48,909 --> 00:53:51,912
THE WOMAN I LOVE DISAPPEARS
AND THEN ABOUT 19 YEARS LATER,

640
00:53:51,912 --> 00:53:55,415
SHE GETS MURDERED,
LEAVING HER DAUGHTER WITH ME
AS WELL AS $200 MILLION.

641
00:53:55,916 --> 00:53:57,918
$200 MILLION?

642
00:53:58,418 --> 00:54:01,421
THAT'S THE BALANCE
OF THE GIRL'S BANK ACCOUNT.
BUT DON'T WORRY,

643
00:54:01,421 --> 00:54:04,908
AT THE RATE SHE SPENDS IT,
I DON'T THINK IT WILL
LAST TOO LONG.

644
00:54:04,908 --> 00:54:06,910
OH, COME ON, MAN.
200 MILLION IS A LOT.

645
00:54:07,410 --> 00:54:10,413
A BUNCH OF MORONS
WITH GLASSES TAILED US
WHEN WE LEFT THE BANK,

646
00:54:10,413 --> 00:54:12,415
