A CERTAIN CURIOSITY.

647
00:54:12,415 --> 00:54:14,417
I SUPPOSE, YEAH.
$200 MILLION.

648
00:54:14,918 --> 00:54:16,920
"WHERE IT ALL BEGAN,
 WHERE IT ALL WILL END."

649
00:54:16,920 --> 00:54:18,905
IT'S NO ACCIDENT
I'M IN MIKO'S WILL.

650
00:54:18,905 --> 00:54:21,908
SHE KNEW I WOULD BE NEEDED,
I JUST KNOW IT.
[ Sighs ]

651
00:54:22,409 --> 00:54:25,912
